          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How long does it take to sell a house in Middle Park?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "Middle Park homes typically sell within 28 to 42 days when priced correctly and presented well. Low suburb turnover works in sellers' favour: buyers who have been watching for months tend to move decisively when a quality property appears. Overpricing relative to actual Middle Park sales evidence is the main risk."
            }
